{"tid":1332131,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"岑子杰陳志全到平機會投訴蔣麗芸歧視同性戀","createTime":"2019-07-19T07:56:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-19T08:14:15.000Z","uid":212626,"like":24,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"64ce398b1aeee0e0aa358f7fcdf8095d7e67ca18","tid":1332131,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T07:56:25.000Z","msg":"民建聯立法會議員蔣麗芸早前在社交網站，呼籲網民廣傳有關民陣召集人岑子杰是同性戀者的短片。人民力量立法會議員陳志全與岑子杰，下午向平機會投訴蔣麗芸歧視同性戀，遞交超過2000個網上聯署。<br />\n<br />\n蔣麗芸在7月1日分享一則來自「教徒心聲」的影片，短片內容的片頭出現「岑子杰，我才得知這位新任的召集人原來是一位同性戀者」字眼，以及一群男扮女裝的男子相片，帖文提及是「重要消息」，並呼籲網民將消息廣傳，有關帖文現已被删除。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1469241-20190719.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1469241-20190719.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=iVbTvSvdcfz%2Fe2yCQDPMV9qUVvxpOm%2FTDjh67WAJGsM%3D&h=c587c475\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1469241-20190719.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=32556855\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1469241-20190719.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fe9e94dd00c766c066c94843e59a7a86efaeece","tid":1332131,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T07:57:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T4vEUG4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT4vEUG4.png&h=59659005&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Cwz2StK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCwz2StK.png&h=e79cfe51&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"df723e36a4802f0bfc4c88194a0901e9abd3b8b3","tid":1332131,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T08:08:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"196fc948f0cf771ed9265d23fa491ed17d2b39c8","tid":